				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%C3%A1t-ai-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-8-C%E1%BB%91-h%E1%BB%AFu-b%E1%BB%99c-x%E1%BA%A1-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-qu%E1%BB%91c-Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-C%E1%BB%ADu-Linh/poem-OMzIcEXGWASbO9P2feqjhw">Bát ai thi kỳ 8 - Cố hữu bộc xạ tướng quốc Trương Cửu Linh - 八哀詩其七－故右僕射相國張公九齡</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-n%E1%BB%99i-c%C3%A1c/poem-Jn21FR6HMHiKqDJJiLzhbA">Đề nội các - 題內閣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-lfkyiRMg6zwt6_eiwas6Yg">Vũ Phạm Khải</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Xu%C3%A2n-%C3%94n/Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-h%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BA%A3m/poem-KTwDTR_HTLgJhKZ6K5r-Sg">Hoài đệ hữu cảm - 懷弟有感</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Xu%C3%A2n-%C3%94n/author-MvAX8pIr0uu6mqdrhe1jhA">Nguyễn Xuân Ôn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BA%A1o/Minh-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-gia-hu%E1%BA%A5n/poem-3aa2tlihTrwlAHWnLopSow">Minh Đạo gia huấn - 明道家訓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BA%A1o/author-f6hExEIODG8dBbnhIj50jQ">Trình Hạo</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/M%E1%BB%99-thu-u%E1%BB%95ng-B%C3%B9i-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Ch%C3%A2u-th%E1%BB%A7-tr%C3%A1t-su%E1%BA%A5t-nh%C4%A9-khi%E1%BB%83n-h%E1%BB%A9ng-k%C3%BD-c%E1%BA%ADn-tr%C3%ACnh-T%C3%B4-Ho%C3%A1n-th%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1/poem-OBlyRxjh5TCqFh5dGFYn3g">Mộ thu uổng Bùi Đạo Châu thủ trát, suất nhĩ khiển hứng, ký cận trình Tô Hoán thị ngự - 暮秋枉裴道州手札，率爾遣興，寄近呈蘇渙侍御</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Qu%C3%BD-C%C3%A1p/S%C4%A9-phu-t%E1%BB%